{"tid":2189483,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[研究] Wi-Fi router關閉5G之後 2.4G信號明顯增強,穿牆能力改善","createTime":"2020-09-05T02:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T18:07:40.000Z","uid":4672,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d10d0f3bc2ebaef53b7a0ae5a478dd1a48e134","tid":2189483,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"如題 原本屋企個廁所係收得1格信號<br />\n今日試過關閉咗5G mode之後 信號即刻滿格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngoogle研究咗一陣之後 發現原理是咁的 <br />\n當一個router有6條接收天線<br />\n開5G情況下 就2.4G 5G會各分配3條 <br />\n但關閉5G之後 全部天線均分配比2.4G 所以信號增強咗<br />\n<br />\n屋企有收唔到wifi死位巴打 可以試試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88024bd3011fdc995b6261d15f53c7148ab3f75","tid":2189483,"uid":184233,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"2.4G 慢撚到 <br />\n用返手機上網仲好啦"},{"pid":"b67bb96762b1180a46809e786756a24b936da704","tid":2189483,"uid":31237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"買過個router算啦"},{"pid":"5c18ceadc907a08ef6555006d61968c12797daaf","tid":2189483,"uid":131430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"換天線咪得囉"},{"pid":"f80197b4a6b857fcb1dfc308dbd5d740793b3fa4","tid":2189483,"uid":5159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"部分高階router 支援你訊號弱既時候係2.4G 5.0G 之間自動切換而無需人手控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9576a162712f118e59c27901a2c2a45d590b7978","tid":2189483,"uid":4672,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f80197b4a6b857fcb1dfc308dbd5d740793b3fa4","tid":2189483,"uid":5159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"部分高階router 支援你訊號弱既時候係2.4G 5.0G 之間自動切換而無需人手控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:24:51.